    "body": "Problem:\n\nIn the markdown source they have the format:\n\n\t[BUILD.md](./BUILD.md)\n\nWhich was replaced with:\n\n\t<a href=\"./build/\">build/</a>\n\nWhich was wrong because the pages are at /doc/install/index.html and\n/doc/build/index.html.\n\nSolution:\n\nReplace them with:\n\n\t<a href=\"/doc/build/\">the build page/</a>\n\nReference: #443\n",
